{"tid":1393791,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":" [代post][長文慎入] 美國戰線: 如何推美國 «香港民主人權法» 和 «重新評估香港政策法» 美國撚請入","createTime":"2019-08-01T08:02:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T13:16:10.000Z","uid":287254,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a7771aae03e63653e2443da85d8928cd3fa37166","tid":1393791,"uid":287254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:02:37.000Z","msg":"聯署去白宮未有用住，因為白宮是總統辦公室。美國三權分立，目前立法未去到呢個步驟，所以白宮只會覆我哋目前佢做唔到啲咩。<br />\n<br />\n基本資料<br />\n<br />\n美國國會(即是參議院及眾議院) 現在有3條關於香港的草案(即是尚未通過的草擬法案) ：<br />\n<br />\n參議院2條 <br />\nS.1838 &lt;香港人權及民主法2019&gt;<br />\n 和<br />\nS.1824 &lt;重新評估香港政策法2019&gt;。<br />\n<br />\n眾議院1條 H.R.3289 &lt;香港人權及民主法2019&gt;。<br />\n<br />\n這3條都是跨黨派(bipartisan)草案，即是民主、共和兩黨都有議員提出和支持。<br />\n<br />\n本屆國會會期是2019年1月3日至2021年1月3日。但目前國會休會6星期，9月復會。所以休會這段時間是 聯絡議員的好時機，希望他們復會時就可以推。<br />\n<br />\n美國立法程序 (簡化版)<br />\n1. 眾議院外交事務委員會三讀通過 (需要至少過半數委員會內的議員投贊成票)<br />\n<a href=\"https://foreignaffairs.house.gov/members\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforeignaffairs.house.gov%2Fmembers&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl56ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=a1d97fc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://foreignaffairs.house.gov/members</a><br />\n2. 眾議院大會三讀通過 (需要435議員中至少218議員投贊成票)<br />\n3. 參議院外交關係委員會三讀通過 (需要至少過半數委員會內的議員投贊成票)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foreign.senate.gov/about/membership\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foreign.senate.gov%2Fabout%2Fmembership&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl56ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=a19eb9a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.foreign.senate.gov/about/membership</a><br />\n4. 參議院大會三讀通過(需要100議員中至少51議員投贊成票)<br />\n5. 十日內總統簽署(或否決): 這才是要推白宮之時<br />\n6. 成為法案<br />\n<br />\n目前處境<br />\n<br />\n在兩院都必須要有足夠議員贊助(co-sponsor)這3條草案，兩院的外交事務/關係委員會才會開始睇。而家仲未夠議員贊助，所以要推 ( = 聯絡議員)<br />\n<br />\nQ &amp; A: <br />\n<br />\nQ1 :需要多少議員贊助？取決於草案內容如何影響美國人民整體利益，影響力越廣泛、需要的co-sponsor議員越多，因此沒有具體答案，總之越多越好。<br />\n<br />\nQ2: 誰人可以幫忙?<br />\n<br />\n有美國住址就得，不一定是公民。可以是永久居民(綠卡持有人)、留學生、在美工作等等。如果你有親朋好友在美國，請幫推。如果你或他/她們是美國公民及已登記選民，請聯絡議員時講明，就會更有幫助。記住如果你有friend子在美國，就算不是香港人，都可以幫手聯絡議員。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>跟住要點做 (重點來了)</strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 找出你住的州和選區的議員及其聯絡方法。<br />\n- 眾議員每個選區1名，請上<a href=\"https://www.house.gov/，然後再右上角輸入5位數字郵政號碼就找到。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.house.gov%2F%EF%BC%8C%E7%84%B6%E5%BE%8C%E5%86%8D%E5%8F%B3%E4%B8%8A%E8%A7%92%E8%BC%B8%E5%85%A55%E4%BD%8D%E6%95%B8%E5%AD%97%E9%83%B5%E6%94%BF%E8%99%9F%E7%A2%BC%E5%B0%B1%E6%89%BE%E5%88%B0%E3%80%82&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl56ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=a9265afa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.house.gov/，然後再右上角輸入5位數字郵政號碼就找到。</a><br />\n- 參議員每個州2名， 請上<a href=\"https://www.senate.gov/senators/contact，然後選你的州就找到。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.senate.gov%2Fsenators%2Fcontact%EF%BC%8C%E7%84%B6%E5%BE%8C%E9%81%B8%E4%BD%A0%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%9E%E5%B0%B1%E6%89%BE%E5%88%B0%E3%80%82&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl56ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=f580bd77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.senate.gov/senators/contact，然後選你的州就找到。</a><br />\n- 所以每人要聯絡3個議員&nbsp;<br />\n- 2個參議員成x 2條草案，和<br />\n- 1個眾議員 x 1條草案<br />\n2. 可以由美國打電話、電郵或寄信給議員<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;a. 打電話<br />\n- 一般會由議員助理聽電話、收信、處理，你同佢講就得。<br />\n- 打電話當然要講英文。<br />\n- 清楚講明草案編號和草案名稱，然後話你想阿乜議員co-sponsor和support這條草案。<br />\n- 佢可能會問你名、地址、電話，佢想知你是否住在佢個選區。請畀真資料，然後你可要求佢保密。<br />\n- 你可要求佢將進度回覆你，你可以話佢知你想佢點覆 (打電話、電郵、回信)。<br />\n- 你順便可以練下英文會話。<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;b. 電郵或寄信<br />\n- 電郵當然要畀你個電郵佢，寄信就畀住址。視乎你想畀/唔畀咩資料。當然寄信要貼郵票啦。<br />\n- 全部要用真名、電話、地址、電郵，但可要求佢保密，因為如果你要求，佢會用你的通訊資料覆你。<br />\n<br />\n以下這三個網頁是這三條法案的詳情和進度以供參考<br />\n<br />\n眾議院H.R.3289 &lt;香港人權及民主法2019&gt;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/house-bill/3289?q=%7B%22search%22%3A%5B%22h.r.3289%22%5D%7D&amp;s=2&amp;r=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F116th-congress%2Fhouse-bill%2F3289%3Fq%3D%257B%2522search%2522%253A%255B%2522h.r.3289%2522%255D%257D%26s%3D2%26r%3D1&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl56ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=5dc16a8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/house-bill/3289?q=%7B%22search%22%3A%5B%22h.r.3289%22%5D%7D&amp;s=2&amp;r=1</a><br />\n<br />\n參議院S.1838 &lt;香港人權及民主法2019&gt;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/senate-bill/1838?q=%7B%22search%22%3A%5B%22s+1838%22%5D%7D&amp;s=1&amp;r=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F116th-congress%2Fsenate-bill%2F1838%3Fq%3D%257B%2522search%2522%253A%255B%2522s%2B1838%2522%255D%257D%26s%3D1%26r%3D1&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl56ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=e4b8ad0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/senate-bill/1838?q=%7B%22search%22%3A%5B%22s+1838%22%5D%7D&amp;s=1&amp;r=1</a><br />\n參議院S.1824 &lt;重新評估香港政策法2019&gt;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/senate-bill/1824?q=%7B%22search%22%3A%5B%22s+1824%22%5D%7D&amp;r=1&amp;s=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F116th-congress%2Fsenate-bill%2F1824%3Fq%3D%257B%2522search%2522%253A%255B%2522s%2B1824%2522%255D%257D%26r%3D1%26s%3D2&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl56ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=c55174a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/senate-bill/1824?q=%7B%22search%22%3A%5B%22s+1824%22%5D%7D&amp;r=1&amp;s=2</a><br />\n<br />\n請先向兩院議員推，兩院通過才推白宮。請快推，因為所有草案都要排隊上兩院相關委員會先，然後上大會。唔想再等就請大大力推。<br />\n<br />\n守護家園&nbsp; 港人有責<br />\n<br />\n利申: 不是Law撚，有錯勿插，請幫手改。"},{"pid":"72d1efe91ccee2a496f3558e6e59ce7be0968028","tid":1393791,"uid":287254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:03:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd52fa569f127438cb43958454743978fc05c5f4","tid":1393791,"uid":287254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:04:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56f2718b38331092367c39fd5cbfd891dad078cd","tid":1393791,"uid":122988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcdc6b9cb45fbeec7a58eb604c26b3be34b18e22","tid":1393791,"uid":235437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:15:39.000Z","msg":"又真係幾長下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d71f7c817d9784bef29a6e2c7cd300c5c73209","tid":1393791,"uid":258465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:18:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"172abcc1321ed03d8a2a0aa81a73b73ade296c4c","tid":1393791,"uid":233009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:19:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e5a26a67828c1182a2574e1a2f1e4b4e16c02dc9","tid":1393791,"uid":287254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T08:52:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e679e635ce3781b198414d04d92e732a235a1d9c","tid":1393791,"uid":287254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:49:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"734f2835378358e2e782d001ad454d682e8016cf","tid":1393791,"uid":287254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T13:16:10.000Z","msg":"推"}]}